Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:41.62,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}歌声の止む時は　運命の終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:49.51,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}そうとだけ決めていた　故は分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:57.47,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}金色も褪せるほど　焦がれてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:04.65,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}憧れの輪郭は　遠ざかってくみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:11.99,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}溢れるよ　ほら手のひら　握り返してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:16.45,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(190,200)}痛みと痛みとりがえよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:20.20,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,0)}糧にするんだ　落花の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.92,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(0,200)}全て傷ついて僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:28.29,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,50)}かたどってく　かたちになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:33.84,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(50,200)}目覚めの先で　往こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:38.26,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}ずっと　響かせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:41.62,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}歌声止息之时  就是命运的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:49.51,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}我只知这样的结论  却不知其原因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:57.47,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的渴望之情能使黄金褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:04.65,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而憧憬的轮廓  却似乎渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:11.99,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我思绪漫溢  快来握紧我的手心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:16.45,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(190,200)}用苦痛来交换苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:20.20,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,0)}用落花残片充当食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.92,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(0,200)}我用所有创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:28.29,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,50)}模仿着塑造自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:33.84,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(50,200)}向着觉醒的前方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:38.26,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}让歌声永远传唱
Comment: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ending-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:06.35,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still remember you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:08.81,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The time we shared
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:11.39,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The love you gave
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:16.36,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Though everything has changed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:21.07,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You push me to live on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:30.91,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海よりも深い奥底から見守っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:36.50,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かれた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:44.13,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still love you, even though I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:53.06,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永久に続く悲しみの夜の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:57.90,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛は生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:03.57,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I will be here for you, always and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:09.83,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今もずっと願っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:20.80,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温かいこの闇の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:06.35,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然记得你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:08.81,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得我们共度的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:11.39,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得你给予我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:16.36,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管一切都已面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:21.07,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你仍是我活着的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:30.91,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自比海更深的幽穴深底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:36.50,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守护着各自分歧的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:44.13,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然爱着你  即使我只能思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:53.06,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在通向永恒的哀恸深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:57.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}犹自有爱存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:03.57,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会为你守在这里  始终如一  直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:09.83,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我仍将继续为你祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:20.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这温暖的黑暗之中
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sign-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:17.89,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.93,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小孩子很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.00,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雕刻她使我极其过瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.21,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有幸整饰这枚乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.25,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}带给我绝顶的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.17,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去吧  人类孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.01,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要你与石头同在  价值就会延续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.42,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家一起上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.46,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.20,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.18,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.32,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}铁丝队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:20.61,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}压住它！
